query:
SELECT
                p.id AS "id!: Uuid",
                p.name AS "name!",
                p.metadata AS "metadata!: serde_json::Value",
                p.created_at AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
            FROM projects p
            INNER JOIN team_projects tp ON p.id = tp.project_id
            WHERE tp.team_id = $1
            ORDER BY p.name ASC
